history.content:
I'm a transfer student and the answer is no (the last time I check it was a year ago).

You can check updated http://web2.assist.org/web-assist/welcome.html .

But I'm pretty sure it's still not transferable. 16B is uniquely designed and combines knowledge from different areas of EE. Courses at CC won't usually do this.
